# Garga, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Garga (; , Gaarga) is a rural locality (an ulus) in Kurumkansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 55 as of 2010.
Geography
Garga is located 38&nbsp;km northeast of Kurumkan (the district's administrative centre) by road. Zaimka Amatkhan is the nearest rural locality.
